# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# File     : GRND019-two-policy-conflict-policy.ttl
# Domain   : Deontic Ontology / ODRL Grounding
# Problem  : Two policies conflict: competing Rights from distinct assigners
# Refs     : Mohammed et al., What Does ODRL Mean? FOIS 2026
# Generated: 2026-03-26 by gen_foundation_problems.py
# Links    : Discriminating/GRND019-two-policy-conflict-1.p
#            Discriminating/GRND019-two-policy-conflict-1.smt2
